Job Description
Mechanical Engineer
My client a leading Drilling Service company are recruiting an Mechanical engineer
with hands-on exposure in various offshore/onshore construction projects, such as; jack-up drilling rigs, jacking vessel, modules.
Must have offshore experience and experience on the below products 5 years minimum total experience
Mud Pumps
Jacking Systems
Brakes - Hydromatic & Electric
Choke/Kill/Standpipe Manifolds
Crowns
Drawworks Repair & Recertification
Hydraulic Axial Piston Pumps
Gears, Shafts & Gear Boxes
My client offers an excellent competitive salary, with a great offshore allowance, full expat package including medical, visa, housing ECT.
